node.title: Trains between Wellington and Kapiti Coast cancelled after slip
node.description: A major slip has forced the cancellation of train services between Wellington and the Kapiti Coast.
node.content: ["A major slip has forced the cancellation of train services between Wellington and the Kapiti Coast.", "Metlink says its trains cannot travel north of Plimmerton because of a slip between Pukerua Bay and Paekakariki.", "It is replacing its services between Plimmerton and Waikanae with buses.", "Last week a train struck a landslide in the same area, closing the tracks temporarily and prompting speed restrictions on the line this week.", "RNZ", "\u00a0"]
